201cKnowledge Frees\u201d to the world, the site also has versions in four languages: Portuguese, English, Spanish and French.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>With the aim of improving the experience of those who access the Instituto Neymar Jr&#8217;s online platform, the project&#8217;s website has a new look. The site was conceived and programmed by the digital marketing agency M3 Social, aiming to improve navigability and offer faster and easier access to those looking for information about the INJR. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":13331,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":true,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[10],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13334"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13334"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13334\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13335,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13334\/revisions\/13335"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13331"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13334"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13334"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13334"}],"cu